-- Anhui Conch Cement Says Ping An Trust Reduces Stake to 6.54% From 11.54%
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-10T22:45:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-10/anhui-conch-cement-says-ping-an-trust-reduces-stake-to-6-54-from-11-54-.html
Anhui Conch Cement Co. said Ping An
Trust & Investment Co. sold 176.6 million shares of the cement
company as of Oct. 8, according to a statement to Shanghai’s
stock exchange.  Ping An Trust’s stake in Anhui Conch was reduced to 6.54
percent from 11.54 percent, according to the statement. Ping An
Trust doesn’t exclude the possibility of selling more shares in
the next 12 months, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  